Wife of the President, Aisha Buhari has reacted to the ongoing trending issue about Pastor Biodun Fatoyinbo sending the police after Mrs Busola Dakolo and her husband Timi Dakolo for falsely accusing him of rape. The development is generating reactions on social media and the wife of the President has in a tweet alerted the IG of police that Justice must prevail for rape victims, and that no one should be intimidated. See her tweet below: ATTENTION : INSPECTOR GENERAL OF POLICE #SayNoToRape #JusticeForRapeVictims #SayNoToIntimidation https://t.co/d4CfmDsntG